Show HN: WebhookStore = Yopmail for webhooks. Now available for teams
text:
WebhookStore is basically Yopmail for webhooks. Free and Open source, for dev purpose.
Any *.webhook.store is a public disposable url.  Personal store: $YOU.github.webhook.store
Team store: $ORG.github-org.webhook.store
